properties.Name: ChannelAggregateProductReturns
properties.Description:
The total Product returns expressed in terms of unit quantity and cancellations valuation for the associated timestamp.

Returns represents the return of product by the customer after it has been billed and delivered.   In this case returns are summarized for a product across all customers.

Columns.Name: ChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: Timestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the associated information is reported, recorded or effective as-of.

Columns.Name: TotalReturnedProductUnitsQuantity
Columns.Description: The total quantity of Product returned for the associated date.

Columns.Name: TotalReturnedProductUnitsValuationAmount
Columns.Description: The total valuation of Product returned during the associated period and valued at actual invoiced price.
